    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good, honest condition and has clearly been well-cared for by its previous owner. The exterior paint still holds a lovely shine, though upon close inspection, you will notice some minor stone chips on the hood and a few light surface scratches consistent with regular use. Inside, the cabin is clean and well-maintained; the leather seats show some light creasing but remain very comfortable with no tears or odors. Mechanically, it is sound and drives beautifully, having received regular servicing throughout its life. It's a reliable, attractive car that is ready for its next owner to enjoy immediately.",
