      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant attention from its next owner. The exterior shows noticeable rust and body damage, while the interior has heavy wear and tear on the upholstery. Mechanically, the engine struggles to maintain a consistent idle and the transmission exhibits rough shifting, making it most suitable as a project car or for parts. It is recommended that any potential buyer brings a trailer, as its reliability for long-distance driving is not guaranteed.",
