    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready to hit the road in this fantastic find! This car is in great shape and has been well-cared for, offering a smooth and reliable driving experience. While it shows some light, honest wear from being enjoyed, it remains a solid, dependable vehicle that's ready for its next adventure. It's a wonderful opportunity to own a high-quality car that still has plenty of life and spirit left!",
